    <title>SSH Git多账号配置 一分钟上手</title>
    <link href="https://zky-luke.github.io/2019/03/06/Article1/"/>
    <id>https://zky-luke.github.io/2019/03/06/Article1/</id>
    <published>2019-03-06T11:40:17.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-06-21T08:40:00.782Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="使用介绍"><a href="#使用介绍" class="headerlink" title="使用介绍"></a>使用介绍</h1><p>默认情况下，一台电脑只有一个SSH Key，假如我们有多个Github账号，需要将代码迁移账号，这时候这篇文章就派上用场啦~</p><h1 id="简单上手"><a href="#简单上手" class="headerlink" title="简单上手"></a>简单上手</h1><h2 id="一、生成秘钥公钥"><a href="#一、生成秘钥公钥" class="headerlink" title="一、生成秘钥公钥"></a>一、生成秘钥公钥</h2><p>装好Git后，桌面右键点击Git Bash进入Git界面，输入以下命令：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">//切换到ssh目录</span><br><span class="line">cd ~/.ssh</span><br><span class="line">//新建两个账户的ssh-key</span><br><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C 10000@qq.com</span><br><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C 20000@qq.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="https://thumbnail0.baidupcs.com/thumbnail/6ebce21c0f2684da94a1b0b3e68389f2?fid=3360643507-250528-482866487959044&rt=pr&sign=FDTAER-DCb740ccc5511e5e8fedcff06b081203-fFd6U9hnDdHp7f5iVudaw1wp668%3d&expires=8h&chkbd=0&chkv=0&dp-logid=3981973583525071722&dp-callid=0&time=1561104000&size=c1280_u720&quality=90&vuk=3360643507&ft=image&autopolicy=1" alt="1.png" title>                </div>                <div class="image-caption">1.png</div>            </figure><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="https://thumbnail0.baidupcs.com/thumbnail/493baedde40fedbf0316a31c4d98cfe3?fid=3360643507-250528-227889363012651&rt=pr&sign=FDTAER-DCb740ccc5511e5e8fedcff06b081203-g%2bJiu8zMmQhxQ6R2FuRSgvU%2fav8%3d&expires=8h&chkbd=0&chkv=0&dp-logid=3981973583525071722&dp-callid=0&time=1561104000&size=c1280_u720&quality=90&vuk=3360643507&ft=image&autopolicy=1" alt="2.png" title>                </div>                <div class="image-caption">2.png</div>            </figure><p>上面先填写Git账户的ssh-key的名称（默认是id_rsa）,下一步则是填写密码及确认密码，不需要密码的话可以直接回车即可。<br>在ssh文件夹已经生成文件，如下<br><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="https://thumbnail0.baidupcs.com/thumbnail/8e405ab39c64194bc46b1ae976b7943b?fid=3360643507-250528-165409894316938&rt=pr&sign=FDTAER-DCb740ccc5511e5e8fedcff06b081203-HroqfH9zoh4f5NnMnLGMgJRb%2f0k%3d&expires=8h&chkbd=0&chkv=0&dp-logid=3981973583525071722&dp-callid=0&time=1561104000&size=c1280_u720&quality=90&vuk=3360643507&ft=image&autopolicy=1" alt="3.png" title>                </div>                <div class="image-caption">3.png</div>            </figure></p><h2 id="二、查看秘钥并放到Github账户"><a href="#二、查看秘钥并放到Github账户" class="headerlink" title="二、查看秘钥并放到Github账户"></a>二、查看秘钥并放到Github账户</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">// 查看秘钥</span><br><span class="line">cat id_rsa_test.pub</span><br><span class="line">cat id_rsa_test2.pub</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="https://thumbnail0.baidupcs.com/thumbnail/f5bf8c4760d55931cef4178d8c3d2d6c?fid=3360643507-250528-335359646666457&rt=pr&sign=FDTAER-DCb740ccc5511e5e8fedcff06b081203-UeviQpO5uVYd8bxSZmZtrSal1Fw%3d&expires=8h&chkbd=0&chkv=0&dp-logid=3981973583525071722&dp-callid=0&time=1561104000&size=c1280_u720&quality=90&vuk=3360643507&ft=image&autopolicy=1" alt="4.png" title>                </div>                <div class="image-caption">4.png</div>            </figure><p>分别添加到两个github账户，详细步骤百度大大搜一搜哈</p><h2 id="三、在ssh目录下创建config并配置"><a href="#三、在ssh目录下创建config并配置" class="headerlink" title="三、在ssh目录下创建config并配置"></a>三、在ssh目录下创建config并配置</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">// 创建config</span><br><span class="line">touch config</span><br><span class="line">// 查看当前目录</span><br><span class="line">ls</span><br><span class="line">// 编辑config</span><br><span class="line">vim config</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="https://thumbnail0.baidupcs.com/thumbnail/d04b2799d9e57f84b2c4557d1e393f4c?fid=3360643507-250528-711104266899741&rt=pr&sign=FDTAER-DCb740ccc5511e5e8fedcff06b081203-ZnmM%2fxzjMoqPMYVLWaglZJ306rc%3d&expires=8h&chkbd=0&chkv=0&dp-logid=3981973583525071722&dp-callid=0&time=1561104000&size=c1280_u720&quality=90&vuk=3360643507&ft=image&autopolicy=1" alt="5.png" title>                </div>                <div class="image-caption">5.png</div>            </figure><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 配置github.com</span><br><span class="line">Host github.com    // 自定义域名地址</span><br><span class="line">    HostName github.com   // 真实域名地址</span><br><span class="line">    IdentityFile C:\Users\Admin\.ssh\id_rsa_test    // id_rsa位置</span><br><span class="line">    PreferredAuthentications publickey    // 权限验证</span><br><span class="line">    User username1    // 用户名</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 配置git.github2.com </span><br><span class="line">Host github2.com </span><br><span class="line">    HostName github.com</span><br><span class="line">    IdentityFile C:\Users\Admin\.ssh\id_rsa_test2</span><br><span class="line">    PreferredAuthentications publickey</span><br><span class="line">    User username2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>写入如上配置，域名和id_rsa位置要根据实际情况填写，然后保存即可。</p><h2 id="四、测试是否配置成功"><a href="#四、测试是否配置成功" class="headerlink" title="四、测试是否配置成功"></a>四、测试是否配置成功</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">// 测试配置</span><br><span class="line">ssh -T git@github.com</span><br><span class="line">ssh -T git@github2.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="https://thumbnail0.baidupcs.com/thumbnail/f13fbe5ba435006babfc0e55bde91c8f?fid=3360643507-250528-698092720352800&rt=pr&sign=FDTAER-DCb740ccc5511e5e8fedcff06b081203-BOqIFs6lG%2b5%2f%2b0taOO338DBArFI%3d&expires=8h&chkbd=0&chkv=0&dp-logid=3981973583525071722&dp-callid=0&time=1561104000&size=c1280_u720&quality=90&vuk=3360643507&ft=image&autopolicy=1" alt="6.png" title>                </div>                <div class="image-caption">6.png</div>            </figure><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="https://thumbnail0.baidupcs.com/thumbnail/0212c6ae80921e29a6269798be56e4ac?fid=3360643507-250528-551481268337412&rt=pr&sign=FDTAER-DCb740ccc5511e5e8fedcff06b081203-d25N9yHm8iky6RALcx4L4Ji9fqQ%3d&expires=8h&chkbd=0&chkv=0&dp-logid=3981973583525071722&dp-callid=0&time=1561104000&size=c1280_u720&quality=90&vuk=3360643507&ft=image&autopolicy=1" alt="7.png" title>                </div>                <div class="image-caption">7.png</div>            </figure><p>出现上图所示，则表示成功啦~~</p><h1 id="项目迁移"><a href="#项目迁移" class="headerlink" title="项目迁移"></a>项目迁移</h1><p>假如有个旧账号的项目要迁移到新账号，先把旧账号项目的代码克隆下来，在新账号新建个项目，在cmd添加远程仓库的ssh并命名为origin2,使用如下命令强制提交代码，就ok了，好嗨~<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git push -u origin2 master -f</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><figure class="image-bubble">                <div class="img-lightbox">                    <div class="overlay"></div>                    <img src="https://thumbnail0.baidupcs.com/thumbnail/c4fa1fc1ea5f657cd0d3d52f8680ca55?fid=3360643507-250528-759687813749093&rt=pr&sign=FDTAER-DCb740ccc5511e5e8fedcff06b081203-2RMEvRyqNcH5eWdD%2f%2b8xKSZBZrw%3d&expires=8h&chkbd=0&chkv=0&dp-logid=3981973583525071722&dp-callid=0&time=1561104000&size=c1280_u720&quality=90&vuk=3360643507&ft=image&autopolicy=1" alt="8.png" title>                </div>                <div class="image-caption">8.png</div>            </figure>]]></content>
    
